{
  "stem": "2533.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were told what we had to do, and it had to be done proper.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then-- I-- I got on my feet there again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were escorted back-- food-- to have our food, and we were, again, roll-called, counted, and all that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was-- I worked there till the escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, but one, I saw it in the film.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that could've been before us, because the camp was there since May '42.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were brought over there-- I always say 'we' because we were coming, not-- not just one person, me-- in-- in December.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the few months before, what happened there, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But one day-- I can't remember what month it was-- there was-- they called out all the Dutch workers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was about 70 or maybe more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were taken away to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They actually called them out--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Called them out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Called them out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They knew who were Dutch, and they called them out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a mother and a son from the Dutch people, and he was taken away, too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the men, not the Dutch women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she begged him to-- to-- to leave her son.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And oh, that was so tragic there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was a young man in the bakery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he was a Polish boy, Polish Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he stepped out from the line, and he said-- will it be-- I don't know how he said it-- he wanted to go in place of that Dutch-- Dutch boy.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he-- they took him, and they left the Dutch boy with the mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, later on, I don't know, when we escaped.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
